FBIS3-37544 "drsov034_b_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-034 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Zhirinovskiy, Kobelev Announce Reconciliation LD1702224094 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 2000 GMT 17 Feb 94 LD1702224094 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] Vladimir Zhirinovskiy and Viktor Kobelev, the second most influential person in the Liberal Democratic Party [LDPR], today announced their reconciliation in Duma corridors. Yesterday Kobelev announced his resignation from the LDPR faction. Kobelev and Zhirinovskiy recognize that they have insignificant ideological disagreements, but have confirmed their readiness to cooperate in the future.
